		"\t\t\t\t\t\t11. What is the primary focus of ROTC?\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tA. Leadership development and military training.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tB. Teaching in public schools.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tC. Community medical missions.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tD. Environmental campaigns.",
