            "\t\t\t\t\t\t2. Which of the following is used to terminate a C++ statement?\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tA. :\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tB. ;\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tC. .\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tD. ,",
            "\t\t\t\t\t\t3. What is the default return type of the main() function in C++?\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tA. int\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tB. void\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tC. float\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tD. char",
            "\t\t\t\t\t\t4. What is the purpose of a constructor in a C++ class?\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tA. To destroy objects created by the class\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tB. To initialize objects when they are created\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tC. To allocate memory manually\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tD. To call other classes",
            "\t\t\t\t\t\t5. What does cin stand for in C++?\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tA. Console Input\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tB. Common Input\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tC. Class Input\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tD. Character Input",
            "\t\t\t\t\t\t6. What is the correct syntax to declare a variable in C++?\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tA. var int\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tB. int x;\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tC. x int;\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tD. variable x;",
            "\t\t\t\t\t\t7. Which of the following is a valid data type in C++?\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tA. integer\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tB. real\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tC. double\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tD. number",
