            "\t\t\t\t\t\t18. What is the default access specifier for a class member in C++?\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tA. public\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tB. private\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tC. protected\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tD. static",
